{
  "chapter": 151,
  "chapter_summary": "田猎大典当日，项少龙与徐先、鹿公在马车中密议对付吕不韦的策略，提出以嫪毐制衡吕不韦、封'仲父'虚衔迷惑对手的计划。进入王宫后，项少龙与妻妾调情，又与李斯同行详述昨晚惊险经历。管中邪加入后，项少龙以退为进试探其对吕娘蓉婚事的态度，管中邪虚伪应对，暴露其无情本性。最后项少龙与即将升任内史的嫪毐密谈，挑拨其与吕不韦的矛盾，为日后的政治布局埋下伏笔。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_gong",
      "speaker_name": "鹿公",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙辛苦了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lu_gong",
      "text": "身体虽累，心情却是愉快的。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_xian",
      "speaker_name": "徐先",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙一副成竹在胸的样子，不知又有什么新的进展？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_gong",
      "speaker_name": "鹿公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黏到喉咙的毒丸都教少龙弄出来，可见老天爷对我大秦确是另眼相看。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_xian",
      "speaker_name": "徐先",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，我们就依少龙之议，以嫪毐制吕不韦，实行以毒攻毒。说真的，吕不韦治国的本领确是不错，让他得意多几年，到将来储君登位，再把他收拾好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_gong",
      "speaker_name": "鹿公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但在这期间我们须牢抓军权，用心培养人才，对付起这家伙来，就更得心应手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xu_xian",
      "text": "小将有一建议，就是王翦……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_xian",
      "speaker_name": "徐先",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这个不用少龙提醒，我们早留心此子，让他再历练多点时间。唉！王龁老得有点糊涂，好应由后生小子取代。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_gong",
      "speaker_name": "鹿公",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙是否准备接收吕娘蓉这个妞儿，好气死吕不韦和管中邪呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lu_gong",
      "text": "为这事头痛的该是他们。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_xian",
      "speaker_name": "徐先",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但摄政大臣的权势非同小可，那时他等若储君，没有他点头，什么政令都批不下来。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xu_xian",
      "text": "徐相还记得我提过'仲父'的虚衔吗？就拿这来骗骗吕不韦，三天后莫傲归天，那时轮到他阵脚大乱，加上嫪毐又当上内史，吕不韦到时才知是什么一回事呢！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们这队算作什么军哩？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "太后特别吩咐，要我们这三天陪她行猎，项大人说该算什么军呢？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "真想抱他同去打猎，却怕他受不起风寒，只好留在清姊处由奶娘照顾。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项郎啊！让我给你介绍两位新奶娘好吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项郎啊！今晚到我们帐内来好吗？人家想得你很苦哩！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_si",
      "speaker_name": "李斯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "每趟当我见到琴太傅时，都觉得她比纪才女更动人；但当见到纪才女，又感到琴清及不上她。现在终能同时看到两人，才明白什么是春兰秋菊，各擅胜场。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_li_si",
      "text": "李兄今天的心情很好哩！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_si",
      "speaker_name": "李斯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "只是苦中作乐吧！这三天田猎外弛内张，危机重重，小弟的心情可以好得到哪里去。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_si",
      "speaker_name": "李斯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项兄昨晚定是睡得不好，两眼红筋满布，又声音嘶哑，教人担心。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_li_si",
      "text": "我根本没有睡过，何来睡得好不好呢？至于声音嘶哑，则是因喉咙给刮伤，但若没此一伤，就要小命不保。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_si",
      "speaker_name": "李斯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "待会儿定要告诉储君，唉！我愈来愈佩服项兄。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_si",
      "speaker_name": "李斯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "难怪刚才吕不韦来向太后和储君禀告，说要把女儿嫁与项兄，请太后和储君作主，太后当然高兴，储君和我却是大惑不解，原来个中竟有如此微妙曲折。嘿！项兄当不会拒绝吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_li_si",
      "text": "你说我会吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_si",
      "speaker_name": "李斯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我大秦一向惯例，是在田猎时颁布人事上的安排和调动，或提拔新人。项兄向储君提议封吕不韦为仲父之计，确是精彩，既可堵住他的口，又可使他更招人猜疑。储君准备当太后再逼他任命吕不韦为摄政大臣时，便以此法应付。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_li_si",
      "text": "李大人自入宫侍奉储君，我们便少有聚首机会，趁这三天大家该好好相聚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大人为何心神恍惚？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "text": "管大人请借一步说话。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大人有什么话要和卑职说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "text": "刚才李长史来告诉我，吕相有意把三小姐下嫁于我，说不定今天会由太后正式颁布。但我却知三小姐倾心的是管兄，坦白说！无论我将来和管兄各自立场如何，但对管兄的胸襟、气魄和剑术均是衷心佩服的，亦不会计较管兄异日因立场不同与我对立；要嘛！就明刀明枪拼个高下。所以只要管兄一句话，我项少龙立即去向太后和储君表明立场，不敢误了三小姐的终身。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "虚饰的话我管中邪不想说，不过三小姐下嫁项兄一事，却非我可以作主的，更不可因我而破坏。有所求，必有所失，人生就是如此。三小姐年纪尚轻，好使性子，但凭项大人的本领，定可使她甘心相从，项大人莫要再为此心烦。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lao_ai",
      "text": "嫪毐大人神采飞扬，必是官运亨通。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "全赖项大人厚爱提携，储君更明言是项大人全力举荐小人的。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "储君这两天会正式任命小人做内史，以后与项大人合作的机会可多着哩！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lao_ai",
      "text": "吕相知悉此事吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "他昨天才知道，还在太后跟前大发脾气，幸好给太后顶了回去。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lao_ai",
      "text": "嫪兄升官发财，他理该高兴才对，有什么反对的理由？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "他当然不会说反对我当内史，只说我因犯事入宫，如今连升数级，必会惹人闲言。嘿！说到底，还不是想我一生当奴仆。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lao_ai",
      "text": "嫪兄放心，我已在徐相和上将军前为你打点过，保证他们会支持嫪兄。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "嘿……这……这……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lao_ai",
      "text": "吕不韦就是这样的人，你的官愈大，太后和储君愈看重你，他愈妒忌你。但嫪兄暂可放心，一天他除不去我项少龙，便无暇理会你。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 151,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 280
    }
  ],
